  <brief_title>A Study to Assess the Efficacy and Safety of Pagoclone for Adults With Stuttering</brief_title>
  <official_title>A 3 Arm, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Parallel Group Study to Assess the Efficacy,Safety and Tolerability of Pagoclone for Adults With Stuttering</official_title>
