  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A multicenter, randomized, 3 arm, placebo-controlled clinical trial to assess the efficacy,
      safety and tolerability of pagoclone for adults with stuttering.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      A multicenter, randomized, 3-arm, placebo controlled, parallel group study with 24 weeks of
      double blind treatment followed by an 8 week double blind washout and then long-term
      open-label extension phase.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
